<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 20:07:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>耶路撒冷以南疑似刺伤事件造成两人受伤，袭击者开枪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/two-wounded-in-suspected-stabbing-attack-south-of-jerusalem-assailant-shot/0000018c-b1ea-d45c-a98e-bbeeb3070000</link><description>袭击发生后，两名 20 多岁的受害者被送往医院</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 19:51:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/two-wounded-in-suspected-stabbing-attack-south-of-jerusalem-assailant-shot/0000018c-b1ea-d45c-a98e-bbeeb3070000</guid></item><item><title>以色列男子在中部城市罗德刺死幼童</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-stabs-toddler-to-death-in-central-city-of-lod/0000018c-b1a1-d014-a3cd-bbbf8e200000</link><description>警方认为嫌疑人患有精神疾病；男孩的母亲说，这名男子不知从哪里突然跳出来，在没有任何挑衅的情况下刺伤了她在婴儿车里的儿子，也没有试图伤害她</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 18:39:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-man-stabs-toddler-to-death-in-central-city-of-lod/0000018c-b1a1-d014-a3cd-bbbf8e200000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陷入战争，内塔尼亚胡的司法政变卷土重来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-28/ty-article/.highlight/with-israel-at-war-netanyahus-judicial-coup-is-back-with-a-vengeance/0000018c-b146-d45c-a98e-bb4e59d20000</link><description>最初的司法改革计划可能会被搁置，但政府还有更危险的空间，可以不受限制和不被注意地扩大权力。公众心烦意乱，忙着恐慌或聚集在旗帜周围</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 18:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-28/ty-article/.highlight/with-israel-at-war-netanyahus-judicial-coup-is-back-with-a-vengeance/0000018c-b146-d45c-a98e-bb4e59d20000</guid></item><item><title>不负责任地使用抗菌药物构成健康威胁，而不是加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2023-12-28/ty-article/irresponsible-use-of-antimicrobials-poses-a-health-threat-not-gaza/0000018c-b0f2-d45c-a98e-bbfe6e350000</link><description>对以色列士兵可能在加沙感染耐药疾病并将其传播给以色列普通民众的担忧在很大程度上是没有根据的，特别是考虑到更大的担忧——无论加沙在世界范围内，耐药感染一直在上升。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 17:54:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/science-and-health/2023-12-28/ty-article/irresponsible-use-of-antimicrobials-poses-a-health-threat-not-gaza/0000018c-b0f2-d45c-a98e-bbfe6e350000</guid></item><item><title>2023 年是以色列历史上最糟糕的一年——但现在还不是绝望的时候</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/2023-was-the-worst-year-in-israels-history-but-now-is-not-the-time-to-despair/0000018c-b0cd-db94-afbd-b0fd936d0000</link><description>这一年发生了可怕的事件——弥赛亚政府、司法政变和哈马斯大屠杀——使今年成为“内塔尼亚胡年”。然而，尽管情况很糟糕，以色列仍有时间在 2024 年改变路线</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 16:44:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/2023-was-the-worst-year-in-israels-history-but-now-is-not-the-time-to-despair/0000018c-b0cd-db94-afbd-b0fd936d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列应该考虑对黎巴嫩进行地面入侵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/lebanon-cant-control-hezbollah-israel-must-broaden-military-action/0000018c-af85-db94-afbd-affdcae40000</link><description>真主党与哈马斯一样致力于摧毁以色列和实施 10 月 7 日式的暴行，但更具杀伤力。其不断增加的导弹和无人机袭击以及黎巴嫩的消极态度证明以色列有理由进行广泛的自卫报复</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 16:40:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/lebanon-cant-control-hezbollah-israel-must-broaden-military-action/0000018c-af85-db94-afbd-affdcae40000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔任命新以色列监狱管理局局长，违反战时政府条款</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-appoints-new-israel-prison-service-chief-violating-terms-of-wartime-government/0000018c-b0fd-db94-afbd-b0fd39330000</link><description>目前尚不清楚国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔是否有权任命目前担任其安全顾问的科比·雅科比少将，或者是否需要政府做出决定</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 16:38:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-appoints-new-israel-prison-service-chief-violating-terms-of-wartime-government/0000018c-b0fd-db94-afbd-b0fd39330000</guid></item><item><title>以色列裔美国人朱迪·韦恩斯坦·哈盖 (Judi Weinstein Haggai) 于 10 月 7 日被谋杀，据信被哈马斯绑架</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-american-judi-weinstein-haggai-believed-kidnapped-by-hamas-was-murdered-on-oct-7/0000018c-b120-d014-a3cd-bb3ece670000</link><description>10 月 7 日早上，朱迪和她的丈夫加迪在尼尔奥兹基布兹散步时失踪。一周前，家人获悉加迪在袭击当天被谋杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 16:20:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-american-judi-weinstein-haggai-believed-kidnapped-by-hamas-was-murdered-on-oct-7/0000018c-b120-d014-a3cd-bb3ece670000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外长呼吁各国如果需要加沙难民请发送电子邮件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/israels-fm-calls-on-countries-to-email-if-they-want-gaza-refugees/0000018c-b0de-db94-afbd-b0ff9ec70000</link><description>伊莱·科恩在电视上说：“只需写下该国的地址即可。”他补充说，欢迎接纳叙利亚和乌克兰难民的国家也接纳加沙人</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 15:54:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/israels-fm-calls-on-countries-to-email-if-they-want-gaza-refugees/0000018c-b0de-db94-afbd-b0ff9ec70000</guid></item><item><title>原定周四在美国大屠杀博物馆举行的反以色列抗议活动被取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/anti-israel-protest-planned-for-thursday-at-u-s-holocaust-museum-is-canceled/0000018c-b0ec-d45c-a98e-bbec47560000</link><description>在博物馆发表声明后，一个名为“反对种族灭绝医生”的新组织取消了抗议活动，声称“利用大屠杀历史对幸存者和受害者的记忆构成严重冒犯”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 15:42:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/anti-israel-protest-planned-for-thursday-at-u-s-holocaust-museum-is-canceled/0000018c-b0ec-d45c-a98e-bbec47560000</guid></item><item><title>新报告显示，以色列的贫困率是发达国家中最高的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israels-poverty-rate-is-among-the-highest-in-the-developed-world-new-report-shows/0000018c-b055-d45c-a98e-bb5d02af0000</link><description>国家保险研究所的报告显示，2022 年所有人口部门的贫困都会增加，三分之一的以色列家庭生活在粮食不安全之中——这一比例在以色列阿拉伯社会中最高</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 15:37:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israels-poverty-rate-is-among-the-highest-in-the-developed-world-new-report-shows/0000018c-b055-d45c-a98e-bb5d02af0000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫高中校长因同情加沙人的苦难而面临停职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-high-school-principal-faces-suspension-for-sympathizing-with-suffering-of-gazans/0000018c-b09c-db94-afbd-b0fd76a80000</link><description>校长因在 Facebook 页面上发表《国土报》的文章而被传唤参加听证会，该文章批评以色列媒体对加沙人道主义危机缺乏报道</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 15:20:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-high-school-principal-faces-suspension-for-sympathizing-with-suffering-of-gazans/0000018c-b09c-db94-afbd-b0fd76a80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院规定，国家不能歧视想要收养的同性伴侣</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-cant-discriminate-against-same-sex-couples-looking-to-adopt-top-court-rules/0000018c-b0d2-d014-a3cd-bade63a80000</link><description>高等法院裁定，在收养孩子的过程中，异性恋不应优先于同性伴侣</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 14:57:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-cant-discriminate-against-same-sex-couples-looking-to-adopt-top-court-rules/0000018c-b0d2-d014-a3cd-bade63a80000</guid></item><item><title>纳粹掠夺了她的艺术品。 10月7日，哈马斯又偷走了另一件雕塑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/museums-exhibits/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-nazis-looted-her-sculpture-on-october-7-hamas-stole-another-piece/0000018c-afbb-d45c-a98e-afffd7710000</link><description>80 年前被纳粹掠夺的一位法国犹太先驱艺术家的作品究竟属于一位来自伦敦的犹太妇女还是该艺术家的孙女？这件事和10月7日的事件有什么关系呢？</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 14:56:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/travel/museums-exhibits/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-nazis-looted-her-sculpture-on-october-7-hamas-stole-another-piece/0000018c-afbb-d45c-a98e-afffd7710000</guid></item><item><title>联合国报告对西岸权利“迅速恶化”表示遗憾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/un-report-deplores-rapid-deterioration-of-rights-in-west-bank/0000018c-b07c-db94-afbd-b07d3aa50000</link><description>报道称，自10月7日哈马斯袭击以来，约300名巴勒斯坦人在与以色列军队或极端主义定居者的冲突中丧生。联合国专员呼吁以色列确保“有效保护巴勒斯坦社区”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 13:30:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/un-report-deplores-rapid-deterioration-of-rights-in-west-bank/0000018c-b07c-db94-afbd-b07d3aa50000</guid></item><item><title>尼尔奥兹幸存者离开埃拉特酒店，可能不会再回家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nir-oz-survivors-leave-eilat-hotel-face-likelihood-they-wont-be-going-home-again/0000018c-af93-d45c-a98e-afdfcd590000</link><description>“当我们的生活被打破的那一天”和“国家抛弃了我们，好人就在它的位置上” ■ 在酒店找到避难所后，幸存者形成了一种奇怪的新常态，日子过得没有时间表或例行公事—— “长湿婆”为他们失去的一切</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 12:53:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nir-oz-survivors-leave-eilat-hotel-face-likelihood-they-wont-be-going-home-again/0000018c-af93-d45c-a98e-afdfcd590000</guid></item><item><title>Nova狂欢受害者的家属拒绝再保持沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-families-of-the-victims-at-the-reim-party-refuse-to-keep-silent-any-longed/0000018c-acff-d22c-a98c-fcff58b50000</link><description>大屠杀发生后的几个星期里，被害者的父母保持沉默，因悲痛而瘫痪。现在，140 个家庭聚集在一起，要求以色列领导人给出答案。 “没有人有精力去战斗，但我们别无选择。我们被遗弃了，”一位家长说</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 12:52:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-families-of-the-victims-at-the-reim-party-refuse-to-keep-silent-any-longed/0000018c-acff-d22c-a98c-fcff58b50000</guid></item><item><title>泄露的法院判决：内塔尼亚胡的司法政变卷土重来，他的攻击再次爆发</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/leaked-court-decision-netanyahus-judicial-coup-is-back-and-his-attacks-are-unleashed/0000018c-b00a-d45c-a98e-bb4e27290000</link><description>就像美国最高法院关于堕胎裁决的泄密一样，以色列法官对内塔尼亚胡关键司法政变法案的泄密立场值得调查</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 12:20:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/leaked-court-decision-netanyahus-judicial-coup-is-back-and-his-attacks-are-unleashed/0000018c-b00a-d45c-a98e-bb4e27290000</guid></item><item><title>星巴克如何卷入以色列-哈马斯战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/how-starbucks-got-embroiled-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-b043-db94-afbd-b07b8ef20000</link><description>欢迎来到 BDS 2.0：如果你不能抵制一家以色列公司，那就以最站不住脚的理由寻找其他东西来抵制</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 12:04:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/how-starbucks-got-embroiled-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018c-b043-db94-afbd-b07b8ef20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列宣布约旦河西岸货币兑换恐怖组织扣押哈马斯数百万资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-declares-west-bank-money-exchange-terror-org-seizes-millions-of-hamas-funds/0000018c-aff3-db94-afbd-affb65040000</link><description>以色列军队突袭了约旦河西岸的 9 个货币兑换分行，逮捕了 21 名涉嫌向哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织转移资金的巴勒斯坦人。巴勒斯坦人报告说，袭击期间发生冲突，造成一人死亡、多人受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Dec 2023 11:33:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-declares-west-bank-money-exchange-terror-org-seizes-millions-of-hamas-funds/0000018c-aff3-db94-afbd-affb65040000</guid></item></channel></rss>